The paper discusses a framework for efficient delivery of 3D streaming data in tele-immersive systems, which involves computer graphics (cs.GR), multimedia (cs.MM), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CV), and human-computer interaction (cs.HC). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
